<topic id="whr_accessible_image_maps">
  <title>Accessible Image Maps</title>
  <body>
    <bodydiv>
      <p>For image maps, text alternatives are needed on both the <xmlelement>image</xmlelement>
        element itself (to describe the informative context) and on each of the
          <xmlelement>area</xmlelement> elements (to convey the link destination or the action that
        will be initiated if the link is followed). The <xmlelement>xref</xmlelement> content within
        the <xmlelement>area</xmlelement> element contains the intended alternative text or hover
        text for that image map area.</p>
      <codeblock outputclass="language-xml">&lt;imagemap id="gear_pump_map">
  &lt;image href="../images/Gear_pump_exploded.png" id="gear_pump_exploded">
    &lt;alt>Gear Pump&lt;/alt>
  &lt;/image>
  &lt;area>
    &lt;shape>circle&lt;/shape>
      &lt;coords>172, 265, 14&lt;/coords>
      &lt;xref href="parts/bushings.dita#bushings_topic/bushings" 
            format="dita">Bushings&lt;/xref>
  &lt;/area>
  &lt;area>
      &lt;shape>circle&lt;/shape>
      &lt;coords>324, 210, 14&lt;/coords>
      &lt;xref href="parts/ports.dita#ports_topic/sucction_port" format="dita"
        >Suction Port&lt;/xref>
   &lt;/area>
&lt;/imagemap></codeblock>
    </bodydiv>
  </body>
